    <dl>
        <dt>Cold Climates</dt>
            <dd>Icy roads and other hazardous driving conditions are more prevalent, causing an increase in people who choose to stay at home.</dd>
        <dt>Warm Climates</dt>
            <dd>Levels of business are carried out with little to no change in either supply or demand of drivers.</dd>
        <dt>Hot Climates</dt>
